CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776366671
OL,3,CMinister urges Home Office to help
OL,4,Cpassengers 'wrongly denied boarding'
OL,6,FShe states the issue has "caused
OL,7,Fconsiderable distress for those
OL,8,Faffected", with ITV News hearing from
OL,9,Fone woman who says she was prevented
OL,10,Ffrom flying back to Jersey from
OL,11,FGreece, via the UK, until she paid for
OL,12,Fextra documents that should not have
OL,13,Fbeen needed.
OL,15,FThe issue affects Jersey residents who
OL,16,Fare not British or Irish Citizens and
OL,17,Fhold physical permits to prove their
OL,18,Fright to travel.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776366671
OL,3,CMinister urges Home Office to help
OL,4,Cpassengers 'wrongly denied boarding'
OL,6,FSince the UK Government introduced the
OL,7,FElectronic Travel Authorisation (ETA)
OL,8,Fscheme, most visitors have to apply
OL,9,Ffor digital permission to visit the
OL,10,FCommon Travel Area.
OL,12,FWhile this is the case for the UK,
OL,13,Fresidents in the three Crown
OL,14,FDependencies - Jersey, Guernsey, and
OL,15,Fthe Isle of Man - are still issued
OL,16,Fpaper documents to prove their status,
OL,17,Fwith the switchover planned in phases
OL,18,Fbetween this June and early next year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776366671
OL,3,CMinister urges Home Office to help
OL,4,Cpassengers 'wrongly denied boarding'
OL,6,FIn the meantime, Deputy Le Hegarat
OL,7,Fsays they have been left with "a
OL,8,Ffrustrating, temporary situation"
OL,9,Fwhere "airlines and ground handlers
OL,10,Fabroad are misinterpreting UK border
OL,11,Frequirements and wrongly denying
OL,12,Fboarding to Jersey residents who have
OL,13,Fthe correct permission to travel".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776366671
OL,3,CMinister urges Home Office to help
OL,4,Cpassengers 'wrongly denied boarding'
OL,6,FShe adds: "We are working hard to
OL,7,Fresolve this. The UK Home Office and
OL,8,Fthe Jersey Customs and Immigration
OL,9,FService (JCIS) have contacted carriers
OL,10,Fand handling agents to make clear that
OL,11,FJersey-issued permissions are valid.
OL,12,FThis includes providing detailed
OL,13,Finstructions for airline staff and
OL,14,Fborder partners."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776366671
OL,3,CMinister urges Home Office to help
OL,4,Cpassengers 'wrongly denied boarding'
OL,6,FJersey immigration and government
OL,7,Fofficials met with the island's
OL,8,FHonorary Polish Consul on Monday
OL,9,Fmorning (13 April) and have reached
OL,10,Fout to other national representatives
OL,11,Flocally to assess the impact and
OL,12,Fcontact specific airlines or airports
OL,13,Fif needed.
OL,15,FThe Government of Jersey advises
OL,16,Fanyone who holds the correct
OL,17,Fpermissions and is "wrongly denied
OL,18,Fboarding" to ask those authorities to
OL,19,Fcontact the UK's Carrier Support Hub,
OL,20,Fwhich should be able to verify their
OL,21,Fstatus.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
